Package: riskintroapp
Title: Analyse Risk of Introduction of Animal Diseases
Version: 0.0.1.008
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eli", "Daniels", , "eli.daniels@ardata.fr", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("David", "Gohel", , "david.gohel@ardata.fr", role = "aut"),
    person("CIRAD", role = "cph")
  )
Description: The package provides an 'RShiny' application for users to
    estimate the risk of an animal disease being introduced into a given
    geographical region using World Animal Health Information System
    (WAHIS) and user imported data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
